text: Well i am not too sure about this company but their truck drivers sure are hooligans. Driving dangerously, speeding and swerving in and out of traffic. Maybe such an established company can afford to put gps tracker on their company vehicles because they sure have the funds to do that. Maybe one day the materials that customers order will arrive safely for them.
Very good service. I emailed an enquiry on Sunday evening, and by Monday afternoon they were already able to deliver my shelves. Price is also competitive. Thank you for your good work
